Hours M-F i7-7, Saturday 7-6
Staff is really nice.

directions: The one behind the counter is wheelchair accessible. The one upstairs is not.

They're pretty cool people about bathroom issues, and if you use the upstairs restroom no one will know you're not a paying customer. 

But their coffee's pretty good and they have the best cupcakes in town so you won't feel too ripped off if you're a paying customer.
